com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.generic
Interface Script

All Known Implementing Classes:
ScriptImpl
public interface Script

A representation of the model object 'Script'. The Script capability is usually contained within a ScriptUnit. The ScriptUnit usually contains an Artifact for the script/zip/archive, and optionally response file and license file artifacts. ScriptUnits usually contain hosting requirements for OsUnits.

The following features are supported:

  • Command Line
  • Compressed
  • Custom Decompressor
  • Decompress Path

See Also:
GenericPackage.getScript()
